name: Pollen #015 (Minerva)
description: Minerva lives in the darkest part of the Pollen Kingdom. She prides herself on her intellect and wisdom, and spends her days learning all that she can about life, nature, and the nymph experience. Queen Lamia feels that such a nymph need not exist, when Lamia herself is "an intellect above all others." ~ pollenkingdom.com
